ht|l|cp|8|AT|
^b@2^*BMarty Bergen: ^*N|cp||at|The reverse is forcing. Opener could have a great hand such as: |ht|o|CS|6|at|^o{|ih|pSAK5 HAJ54 DAKJ32 C2|at|}|
