{      Forcing or Not - Example 5    }
^-|
ht|d|cs|6|at|^B{|ia|,3Cp3S|at|}|hf|k|lb|*yIs this bid forcing^^N|
ht|l|cp|8|AT|
^b@2^*BMarty Bergen: ^*N|cp||at|Partnership. In Standard, a new suit by an UPH (unpassed hand) after partner's preempt is forcing. I think this is foolish. I treat all new suits after a preempt as nonforcing.|
